description:
**Prerequisites:**
1. Initialize Next.js if needed: `npx create-next-app@latest . --typescript --tailwind --app --src-dir false --import-alias '@/*'`
2. Install core dependencies: `npm install zod react-hook-form @hookform/resolvers date-fns lucide-react better-sqlite3 && npm install -D @types/better-sqlite3`
3. Initialize shadcn/ui: `npx shadcn@latest init` (select: Default style, Neutral slate, CSS variables yes)
4. Add components: `npx shadcn@latest add form input button calendar select card label popover toast`

**Files to create:**

`/lib/types.ts` - Core types and schemas:
```typescript
import { z } from 'zod';

export const RSUEventSchema = z.object({
  employer: z.string().min(1, 'Employer required'),
  vestingDate: z.date({ required_error: 'Vesting date required' }),
  shares: z.number().positive('Shares must be positive').int('Shares must be whole number'),
  fmvUsd: z.number().positive('FMV must be positive').multipleOf(0.01, 'FMV must have max 2 decimals'),
  usState: z.enum(['WA', 'CA', 'NY', 'TX']),
  canadaProvince: z.enum(['BC', 'ON', 'AB'])
});

export type RSUEvent = z.infer<typeof RSUEventSchema>;
```

`/lib/employers/index.ts` - Employer definitions:
```typescript
export const SUPPORTED_EMPLOYERS = [
  { value: 'meta', label: 'Meta', ticker: 'META' },
  { value: 'amazon', label: 'Amazon', ticker: 'AMZN' },
  { value: 'google', label: 'Google', ticker: 'GOOGL' },
  { value: 'microsoft', label: 'Microsoft', ticker: 'MSFT' }
] as const;
```

`/lib/db/init.ts` - SQLite database setup:
```typescript
import Database from 'better-sqlite3';
import path from 'path';

const db = new Database(path.join(process.cwd(), 'taxbridge.db'));

db.exec(`
  CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS rsu_events (
    id TEXT PRIMARY KEY,
    employer TEXT NOT NULL,
    ticker_symbol TEXT NOT NULL,
    vesting_date TEXT NOT NULL,
    shares INTEGER NOT NULL,
    fmv_usd REAL NOT NULL,
    total_value_usd REAL NOT NULL,
    us_state TEXT NOT NULL,
    canada_province TEXT NOT NULL,
    created_at TEXT NOT NULL
  )
`);

export default db;
```

`/components/rsu/rsu-entry-form.tsx` - Main form component (750+ lines):
- Use `useForm<z.infer<typeof RSUEventSchema>>` with `zodResolver(RSUEventSchema)`
- Calendar: `<Popover><PopoverTrigger asChild><Button variant="outline">{format(field.value, "PPP")}</Button></PopoverTrigger><PopoverContent><Calendar mode="single" selected={field.value} onSelect={field.onChange} disabled={(date) => date > new Date()} /></PopoverContent></Popover>`
- FMV Input: Format as currency on blur: `new Intl.NumberFormat('en-US', { style: 'currency', currency: 'USD' }).format(value)`
- Auto-calculate: `const totalValueUsd = watch('shares') * watch('fmvUsd')` with `useEffect` to display
- Submit handler: `async (data) => { const response = await fetch('/api/rsu', { method: 'POST', headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' }, body: JSON.stringify({ ...data, vestingDate: data.vestingDate.toISOString() }) }); if (response.ok) { toast({ title: 'Success', description: 'RSU event saved' }); form.reset(); } else { toast({ title: 'Error', description: 'Failed to save', variant: 'destructive' }); } }`

`/app/api/rsu/route.ts` - API route:
```typescript
import { NextRequest, NextResponse } from 'next/server';
import db from '@/lib/db/init';
import { RSUEventSchema } from '@/lib/types';
import { SUPPORTED_EMPLOYERS } from '@/lib/employers';
import { randomUUID } from 'crypto';

export async function POST(req: NextRequest) {
  try {
    const body = await req.json();
    const validated = RSUEventSchema.parse({ ...body, vestingDate: new Date(body.vestingDate) });
    const employer = SUPPORTED_EMPLOYERS.find(e => e.value === validated.employer);
    const id = randomUUID();
    const totalValueUsd = validated.shares * validated.fmvUsd;

    db.prepare(`INSERT INTO rsu_events (id, employer, ticker_symbol, vesting_date, shares, fmv_usd, total_value_usd, us_state, canada_province, created_at) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)`)
      .run(id, validated.employer, employer!.ticker, validated.vestingDate.toISOString(), validated.shares, validated.fmvUsd, totalValueUsd, validated.usState, validated.canadaProvince, new Date().toISOString());

    return NextResponse.json({ success: true, id });
  } catch (error) {
    return NextResponse.json({ error: error instanceof Error ? error.message : 'Validation failed' }, { status: 400 });
  }
}
```

`/app/rsu-entry/page.tsx` - Page wrapper:
```typescript
import RSUEntryForm from '@/components/rsu/rsu-entry-form';

export default function RSUEntryPage() {
  return (
    <main className="container mx-auto py-10 max-w-2xl">
      <h1 className="text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Add RSU Vesting Event</h1>
      <RSUEntryForm />
    </main>
  );
}
```

**Acceptance Criteria:**
1. Form renders with all fields (vesting date calendar popover, FMV with currency formatting, shares integer input, employer dropdown with Meta/Amazon/Google/Microsoft, US state dropdown WA/CA/NY/TX, Canada province BC/ON/AB)
2. Total value auto-calculates and displays formatted as USD currency
3. Validation errors display inline: negative shares shows 'Shares must be positive', empty employer shows 'Employer required', future dates disabled in calendar
4. Successful submission: POST to `/api/rsu` with payload `{"employer":"meta","vestingDate":"2025-03-15T00:00:00.000Z","shares":100,"fmvUsd":450.50,"usState":"WA","canadaProvince":"BC"}` returns `{"success":true,"id":"[uuid]"}` status 200, toast displays 'Success', form resets
5. Database row inserted: `SELECT * FROM rsu_events WHERE employer='meta'` returns row with shares=100, fmv_usd=450.50, total_value_usd=45050.00, ticker_symbol='META'
6. Failed validation: submitting empty form shows 5 error messages, returns 400 status

